text: "Style" is a song by American singer-songwriter Taylor Swift. It is the third track from her fifth studio album, 1989. It was released as the third single from the album on February 9, 2015. It reached number six on the US Billboard Hot 100. It topped the Mainstream Top 40/Pop Songs chart in the United States. The song contains elements of disco, funk-pop, and pop rock. ==References== Category:Taylor Swift songs Category:2014 songs Category:Pop songs
